These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, december, july
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, iris, bellflower, aconite
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, snooker, backgammon
House: futuristic, colonial, palace, cape-cod
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the colonial house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the palace house is the person who growsiris##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday          | june    | december      | april  | july     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Flower   | iris       | amaryllis | bellflower     | aconite    |
| Game   | backgammon | bridge         | scrabble  | snooker    |
| House           | palace      | cape-cod       | futuristic | colonial |

