.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, spanish, argentine, colombian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, begonia, rose
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, reading, camping
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, tram, scooter, snowmobile
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the colombian is on the far right##1
 5. the pakistani is on the right of the spanish##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
11. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Nationality      | spanish      | pakistani     | argentine    | colombian |
| Flower   | daffodil | amaryllis   | begonia   | rose           |
| Hobby   | singing  | camping     | reading    | board-games         |
| Transport           | snowmobile         | tram | scooter     | van        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

