.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, software-developer, accountant
4 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, poker, scrabble
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, aristoff, old-henry, davidoff
House: farmhouse, ranch-style, cottage, wooden
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the software-developer is the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the cottage house is on the right of the accountant##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the software-developer##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the software-developer is on the right of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Job          | designer    | accountant      | software-developer  | librarian   |
| Game   | scrabble     | poker      | monopoly | snooker      |
| Cigar           | aristoff       | fonseca         | davidoff  | old-henry         |
| House         | farmhouse | ranch-style | cottage  | wooden |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

