.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, backgammon, go
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, turquise, coral, lavender
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, soul, gospel, country
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, security-guard, fisherman, freelancer
 1. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 2. the person playing go is on the left of the security-guard##1
 3. the security-guard is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
 5. the firefighter is on the far left##1
 6. the fisherman is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the freelancer is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Game          | backgammon     | snooker   | go | canasta |
| Color   | turquise | coral | white   | lavender       |
| Music-Genre           | soul       | trance      | country     | gospel |
| Job     | firefighter    | fisherman     | freelancer     | security-guard     |

