 3. the person who's birthday is in july is the blend-smoker##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person eating pomegranate is the blend-smoker##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
10. the pall-mall-smoker is the person eating peach##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
