.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, rose, dahlia
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lavender, aquamarine, blue
There are 4 different nationalities: german, pakistani, turkish, polish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, davidoff, vegafina
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike, van
 1. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the german##1
 2. the person who likes red is the german##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the polish##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
 7. the polish is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the pakistani##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is the alhambra-smoker##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
12. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Flower    | daisy     | lily  | dahlia       | rose      |
| Color       | aquamarine    | blue        | red  | lavender      |
| Nationality         | pakistani  | polish | german | turkish |
| Cigar         | blend | vegafina          | alhambra         | davidoff      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

