.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, biathlon, tennis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, fonseca, cain, pall-mall
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, bellflower, daffodil, aconite
4 different games are played: canasta, go, billiard, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the cain-smoker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
12. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Sport      | tennis       | biathlon      | swimming      | soccer    |
| Cigar         | pall-mall | cain | fonseca | havana  |
| Flower   | daffodil    | bellflower     | aconite      | marigold |
| Game   | billiard  | scrabble     | canasta    | go  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

