.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
City: nizza, venice, paris, san-francisco
House: farmhouse, cottage, wooden, modern
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, argentine, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rowing, skiing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, tea, water
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the wooden house##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the malaysian##1
 5. the malaysian is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the chinese is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person traveling to paris##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
12. the cottage house is on the far right##1
13. the modern house is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| City          | san-francisco      | venice     | nizza        | paris     |
| House         | wooden     | farmhouse    | modern | cottage |
| Nationality   | malaysian | argentine  | chinese      | egyptian       |
| Sport         | rowing      | lacrosse | parkour     | skiing        |
| Beverage     | tea   | water     | fanta  | 7up       |

