.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, scientific, musical, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, game, tiparillo
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, february, september
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, orange, amber
 1. the social-worker is the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the social-worker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the doctor##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the doctor is the person who likes brown##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Movie-Genre        | scientific    | zombie        | disaster        | musical      |
| Cigar       | game       | vegafina       | havana      | tiparillo |
| Job         | entrepreneur | social-worker | security-guard | doctor      |
| Birthday         | october          | september         | june           | february    |
| Color   | orange         | yellow       | amber     | brown   |

 